{"tid":1882351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【沒事兒】蝗蟲逼近中國國境　農業農村部：爆發蝗災風險很低","createTime":"2020-02-16T07:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T13:03:01.000Z","uid":224066,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"aeab54ea5847a31f41cf90404bad52528a163f92","tid":1882351,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"沙漠蝗（Schistocerca gregaria）大軍肆虐東非，並進一步蔓延至巴基斯坦及印度等國，對肯亞、索馬里、巴基斯坦、印度等地造成嚴重的農業災難。聯合國糧農組織（FAO）更向全球預警，希望全球高度戒備當前正在肆虐的蝗災，防止被入侵國家出現糧食危機。<br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲入侵印巴，位置已逼近中國國境線，有人擔心蝗災會否對中國造成危害。對此，農業農村部表示，沙漠蝗對中國的危害概率很小，<span style=\"color: red;\">國內大規模爆發蝗災風險很低。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e48a5d35e00e37651d93613.png/GmnMfJAe11P8Q-zU1KFLkzMi0T9C7H0OU94-xVPePsU?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e48a5d35e00e37651d93613.png%2FGmnMfJAe11P8Q-zU1KFLkzMi0T9C7H0OU94-xVPePsU%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=ccee1f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n農業農村部種植業管理司植保植檢處表示，近年來，中國蝗蟲監測預警和防治能力不斷提升，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">防治技術水平屬於世界領先水平，防蝗藥械儲備充足，國內大面積暴發蝗災風險很低。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前，農業農村部正密切跟踪境外蝗災動態，同時安排雲南、西藏等省區加強邊境的蝗蟲監測，嚴防遷入危害。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e3a5699aa60062bd0ef7a2c.jpg/blbwjGnDNPNanAiEJoCyak-90jp7ieh1Yb93gWG_d4E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e3a5699aa60062bd0ef7a2c.jpg%2FblbwjGnDNPNanAiEJoCyak-90jp7ieh1Yb93gWG_d4E&h=c936f139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另據官方《央視新聞》引述專家指出，中國史料中尚未發生沙漠蝗危害記載，且考慮到中國邊境地區崑崙山脈和喜馬拉雅山脈阻隔，蝗蟲很難越過高海拔的寒冷地區。中國西藏南部和雲南西部邊境與尼泊爾和緬甸沙漠蝗發生區毗鄰，<span style=\"color: red;\">隨季風可能有少量遷入中國，但危害的概率很小。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e3a56994e64212bb85ae066.jpg/yU7-K--35cxmtYGi4hZ25iGILcaB5Z8Zj8nchI_J3IQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e3a56994e64212bb85ae066.jpg%2FyU7-K--35cxmtYGi4hZ25iGILcaB5Z8Zj8nchI_J3IQ&h=5bfb6bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中科院專家：不會對中國形成嚴重威脅</span><br />\n<br />\n中國科學院院士、河北大學校長、生態和昆蟲學家康樂接受《中國科學報》時亦指，中國不是沙漠蝗的分布區，沙漠蝗不會對中國形成嚴重威脅。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，中國曾是世界上遭受蝗災最嚴重的國家，但上世紀50、60年代經過治理，蝗區面積已大幅度縮小，種群密度長期控制著較低水平。在過去的40多年來，雖然在局部地區蝗災時有發生，但是沒有形成遷飛危害和嚴重的經濟損失。<br />\n<br />\n康樂又說，中國開發的真菌生物農藥和群聚拮抗劑可以應用到非洲和「一帶一路」相關國家。實際上，中科院已經與非洲科學院和有關國家的科學家取得了聯繫，正在洽談合作事宜。"},{"pid":"5443565c8957e4803bea97b210779411204e82db","tid":1882351,"uid":194399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"(借位thx) 請各位開發新戰線 : Youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的: 利用youtube演算法, 增加黃絲channel及文宣曝光機會, 降低藍絲文宣的散播速度, 應對中共KOL 100計劃<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲channel&rarr; like、comment、subscribe、share</span><br />\n藍絲channel&rarr; 不感興趣 /不要推薦這個頻道、開1.2秒close(降低續看率)<br />\n<ins>進一步措施</ins> : 利用家中長輩ac dislike + report藍片 &amp;<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 觀看+like黃片</span>, <ins>可提高黃片在其年齡層的曝光度</ins><br />\n<br />\n【中共最新滲透計劃 : KOL 100】    <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1881621\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1881621</a>"},{"pid":"0e081635c71137180ed074368beacf52fac3f4e6","tid":1882351,"uid":104138,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"可防可控"},{"pid":"6ed83b57946f52052402ec06d61c83d231f7f171","tid":1882351,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:57:36.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇講錯嘅<br />\n又真係有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>喜馬拉雅山天然屏障</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人都過唔到更何況蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係印度西面有<br />\n如果蔓延到緬甸都有嘅話，雲南就真係可能有蝗禍啦"},{"pid":"3193ebde4358f432a8b646038e08b434ea785271","tid":1882351,"uid":87723,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79d4fdefe311f42cd15df85aea0afb27a3f355e","tid":1882351,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"可防可控<br />\n有限人傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44688c18b62610433b9e2d14abc485ca097fe56d","tid":1882351,"uid":280136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e79d4fdefe311f42cd15df85aea0afb27a3f355e","tid":1882351,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"可防可控<br />\n有限人傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"驚唔驚蝗蟲？<br />\n<br />\n唔驚！相信政府！<br />\n有政府！有政府唔驚！<br />\n<br />\n咁儲唔儲糧？<br />\n<br />\n唔儲！"},{"pid":"f50978b958cbc52095e962d3eb26b696db9d9262","tid":1882351,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"<em>中國不是沙漠蝗的分布區，沙漠蝗不會對中國形成嚴重威脅。</em><br />\n<br />\n沒事da <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信政府"},{"pid":"c47e9ca27cbd835215090dc7168164777f67ebb8","tid":1882351,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ed83b57946f52052402ec06d61c83d231f7f171","tid":1882351,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:57:36.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇講錯嘅<br />\n又真係有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>喜馬拉雅山天然屏障</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人都過唔到更何況蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係印度西面有<br />\n如果蔓延到緬甸都有嘅話，雲南就真係可能有蝗禍啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:06:54.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲群隨風飛翔，風速大致相同。 它們一天可覆蓋天空飛越100到200公里，並且<span style=\"color: red;\">會飛到海拔2,000米左右，但在更高的高度會太冷。因此，蝗蟲群無法越過阿特拉斯山脈、興都庫什山脈或<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>喜馬拉雅山脈</strong></span>等高山山脈</span>。它們不會冒險進入非洲的雨林，也不會冒險進入中歐。然而，蝗蟲成蟲和成群的蟲群經常穿越非洲和阿拉伯半島之間的紅海，甚至有報導在1987-89年的十天蝗害，它們從非洲到加勒比越過了大西洋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E8%9D%97%E8%9F%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E6%25BC%25A0%25E8%259D%2597%25E8%259F%25B2&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=f3c606cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E8%9D%97%E8%9F%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n印度西面本身都係佢活動範圍<br />\n只不過今年爆得勁啲<br />\n可以觀望一下但暫時唔洗咁大期待<br />\n等啲蝗飛到緬甸先至再慶祝都唔遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afce4eed0bde73bbd4e742d484a8d8ca1b42c604","tid":1882351,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"天國近了 你們應當悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12ee86c12646798b9a5e6489857e3298aaf547d","tid":1882351,"uid":288949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"多多都會成為蚛蟈人食糧<br />\n沒事兒"},{"pid":"2d5f5f98d31f0b6261916d7616a6c830ec16453d","tid":1882351,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rj5cZp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rj5cZp.jpg&h=ce64bf9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4df7529ef58081207befafe8db5f6995552a680","tid":1882351,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"天災嘅嘢好難講嘅.....真係大軍殺到個時，就太遲...."},{"pid":"2900b63b6615d9515028de732673ffbeb0ce8ad4","tid":1882351,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c12ee86c12646798b9a5e6489857e3298aaf547d","tid":1882351,"uid":288949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"多多都會成為蚛蟈人